<section class="section alt"><div class="container"><div class="grid-4"><article class="process-card"><p class="eyebrow">01</p><p>Diagnose operating friction, compliance exposure, and leadership reporting gaps with senior interviews and artifact review.</p></article><article class="process-card"><p class="eyebrow">02</p><p>Design the operating model, control routines, service standards, and dashboard architecture around how the team actually works.</p></article><article class="process-card"><p class="eyebrow">03</p><p>Install practical tools, meeting rhythms, owner maps, and documentation so managers can run the system without consultants in the room.</p></article><article class="process-card"><p class="eyebrow">04</p><p>Stabilize adoption with weekly review, executive readouts, and refinements tied to measurable operating outcomes.</p></article></div></div></section>
